{
  "stem": "12052.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And mine father was even much less religious than my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we just-- my grandfather still observed Saturday, only not in-- completely in a religious style.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He didn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or-- or-- so only we didn't had too much observance any-- any religious where I completely-- I didn't attend any-- any religious classes or any-- I was maybe ready already like a kid, more agnostic than-- than any Jewish-- Jewish faith.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, not at all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the-- till-- till the war, until they separated Slovaks from the Czechs, the-- there was a very good relation.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And matter of fact, we-- we had a contact.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were visited many time by the Russian Orthodox bishop and-- and some of the [NON-ENGLISH], that they were family friends where-- my father also was for a time involved with the politics, of the city politics.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was also one time also in the city council.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was very good relation between non-Jews and Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was no-- no problem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Only when the Slovaks tried to separate-- matter of fact, there was a Catholic president who was a-- a Catholic priest.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was elected.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and he somehow didn't-- he-- he collaborated with-- with the Germans and Hitler.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after the war, they-- he was executed by-- by hanging.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Only a total-- our family, the-- the relation between the Jews and Catholic was-- and there was also a lot of-- a lot of Greek-- not Greek only-- Russian Orthodox Church and members.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had a exceptional good relation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "One of mine uncles, also he-- he was going-- this was before-- I think so-- still in Austria and Hungary.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He attended a Russian Orthodox Church around our school.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
